---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Contact — AiCraft"
  description="Start a conversation about your data, AI, or web project. No jargon, no sales pressure—just a quick look at what you have and what you're trying to decide."
>
  <section class="contact-page section">
    <div class="container contact-inner">
      <div class="contact-text">
        <p class="eyebrow">Let's talk</p>
        <h1 class="contact-heading">Let's talk about your idea or problem</h1>
        <p class="contact-intro">
          If you're curious whether AI, automation, or data apps could actually help your small
          team, the easiest way to find out is a short conversation. No jargon, no sales
          pressure—just a quick look at what you have and what you want to do. 
        </p>
        <p class="contact-intro">
          I can also sit on your side of the table as you evaluate proposals, write statements of work, or decide whether to hire other consultants or vendors.
        </p>
        <br>
        <p class="contact-follow">
          I'll review what you send and reply within two business days with next steps for a more in-depth conversation around your goals.
        </p>

        <div class="contact-expect">
          <p class="contact-expect__label">What usually happens</p>
          <ol class="contact-expect__steps">
            <li>I read your note and reply within two business days.</li>
            <li>If it's a good fit, I suggest a 20-minute call — no obligation.</li>
            <li>We agree on a concrete first step, scoped and priced clearly.</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </div>

      <form class="contact-form" method="POST" data-netlify="true" name="contact" netlify-honeypot="bot-field">
        <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact" />
        <p class="hidden" aria-hidden="true">
          <label>Don't fill this out if you're human: <input name="bot-field" /></label>
        </p>

        <div class="field-row">
          <div class="field">
            <label for="name">Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required autocomplete="name" />
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <label for="email">Email</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required autocomplete="email" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="field-row">
          <div class="field">
            <label for="organization">Organization</label>
            <input type="text" id="organization" name="organization" />
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <label for="role">
              Role
              <span class="field-optional">(optional)</span>
            </label>
            <input
              type="text"
              id="role"
              name="role"
              placeholder="How do you fit into the team?"
              autocomplete="organization-title"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="field">
          <label for="data">What are you working with?</label>
          <p class="field-hint">A sentence or two about your data and tools (e.g., spreadsheets, historical records, forms, website).</p>
          <textarea id="data" name="data" rows="3"></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="field">
          <label for="improve">What would you like to improve?</label>
          <p class="field-hint">One workflow, report, or recurring question you'd love to make easier.</p>
          <p class="field-examples">e.g., "We export a spreadsheet and build a donor report by hand every week — it takes half a day." or "We have 10 years of grant records and nobody can find anything."</p>
          <textarea id="improve" name="improve" rows="4" required></textarea>
        </div>

        <p class="form-trust">I work with small businesses, local governments, and nonprofits. If you're not sure this is a fit, ask anyway.</p>

        <button type="submit" class="button button--primary submit-btn">Send this to AiCraft</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .contact-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.6fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .contact-heading {
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .contact-intro {
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .contact-follow {
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.65;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
  }

  .contact-expect {
    padding: 1.25rem 0 0;
  }

  .contact-expect__label {
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.07em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
  }

  .contact-expect__steps {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
    counter-reset: steps;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.625rem;
  }

  .contact-expect__steps li {
    counter-increment: steps;
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .contact-expect__steps li::before {
    content: counter(steps);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    background: rgba(23, 23, 23, 0.07);
    width: 1.375rem;
    height: 1.375rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }

  .contact-form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hidden {
    display: none;
  }

  .field-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .field {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.375rem;
  }

  label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }

  .field-optional {
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    margin-left: 0.25rem;
  }

  .field-hint {
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
    font-size: 0.825rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .field-examples {
    margin: 0 0 0.375rem;
    font-size: 0.825rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.55;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .form-trust {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  input[type="text"],
  input[type="email"],
  textarea {
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    transition: border-color var(--duration-fast) var(--ease-standard);
    width: 100%;
    -webkit-appearance: none;
  }

  input[type="text"]:focus,
  input[type="email"]:focus,
  textarea:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--color-ink);
    background: #ffffff;
  }

  textarea {
    resize: vertical;
    min-height: 80px;
  }

  .submit-btn {
    align-self: flex-start;
    padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .contact-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .field-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
